    <p><strong>Retention/static note:</strong> Retention stays low; static is usually mild unless beans are very light and dry.</p>
    <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CJ4YFMQ9" external>Check Q Air price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>

    <h3>3) TIMEMORE Chestnut C2 — Best for pressurized-basket espresso starters</h3>
    <p><strong>Verdict:</strong> Best value if your espresso machine uses pressurized baskets and you want reliable grind quality per dollar.</p>
