    <p><strong>Skip this if...</strong> your main goal is non-pressurized espresso consistency every day.</p>
    <p><strong>Espresso realism:</strong> Pressurized baskets: solid. Non-pressurized baskets: click jumps are often too coarse for clean repeatability.</p>
    <ProsCons
