    <p><strong>Retention/static note:</strong> Retention is low, but fines can cling internally if cleaning cadence slips.</p>
    <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0833SDN8M" external>Check C2 price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>

    <h3>4) HARIO Smart G Pro — Best travel hand grinder under $100 for espresso kits</h3>
    <p><strong>Verdict:</strong> Good backup/travel grinder when weight and portability matter more than shot precision.</p>
    <p><strong>Buy this if...</strong> you want a lightweight manual grinder for travel with portable espresso makers.</p>
    <p><strong>Skip this if...</strong> you want quick grinding and dependable non-pressurized shot control.</p>
    <p><strong>Espresso realism:</strong> Better for pressurized baskets; this model's internal stepped adjustment has wider jumps that limit true espresso control.</p>
